<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hold-up">hold up</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>举起；抬起；支撑：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>hold up one's hand
举起手</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The roof is held up by wood.
屋顶由木头支撑着。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>支持住；承受住：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She's held up well under the pressure.
她承受住了压力。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>使停顿；停止下来：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bus got held up in traffic.
公共汽车被堵在了路上。</p><footer>外研⑧ - 4</footer></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>举出（例子）；提出（作为榜样）</strong></h4></div>